  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/07/03/apple-reportedly-hires-hulu-exec-to-negotiate-future-media-deals/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/pete-distad-hulu.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n一间科技公司要找多媒体业界合作似乎并不容易，早前就传闻 Apple 在推出 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/iTunesRadio/\">iTunes Radio</a> 之前曾花了<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/07/apple-reportedly-lands-sony-deal-for-radio-service-ahead-of-wwdc/\">不少力气</a>去说服业界合作，就像聘请前 YSL CEO <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/PaulDeneve/\">Paul Deneve</a> 一样，直接找多媒体业界人士来做这件苦差事可能来得比较简单。据 Bloomberg 报导，Apple 已经招揽了 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Hulu/\">Hulu</a> 的市场及销售部 SVP Pete Distad，未来的工作就是为 Apple 争取多媒体业界的合作。另外，同一个来源亦指出 Apple 快要跟 Time Warner Cable 签约，在几个月内会为 Apple TV 用户带来后者的「订阅」服务。不过目前没有任何一样公司对上述传闻作出评论呢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/07/02/apple-reportedly-hires-hulu-exec-to-negotiate-future-media-deals/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-02/apple-said-to-near-time-warner-cable-deal-for-tv-programs.html\">Bloomberg</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/03/apple-reportedly-hires-hulu-exec-to-negotiate-future-media-deals/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20645711/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/03/apple-reportedly-hires-hulu-exec-to-negotiate-future-media-deals/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
